<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ل هـ ب<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٤٦٢٧ - ل هـ ب]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لهِبَ يلهَب، لَهَبًا ولَهيبًا، فهو لاهب ولَهْبانُ/ لَهْبانٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• لهِبتِ النَّارُ:</span> اشتعلت خالصةً من الدُّخان.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• لهِب الشَّخْصُ:</span> عطِش <span class="c1">"لهِب من حرارة الجَوّ"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>